.
 If this is set to 
\begin_inset Formula $R$
\end_inset

, then 
\begin_inset Formula $s=\frac{{R}}{pG+(1-p)B}$
\end_inset

.
 For good returns, tenant gets 
\begin_inset Formula $G-R$
\end_inset

