 So to not break the contract we must have 
\begin_inset Formula $L>G$
\end_inset

 i.e.
 
\begin_inset Formula $U(H)-U(M)\le N[U(M)-\{pU(H)+(1-p)U(L)\}]+S$
\end_inset

 (social sanctions = 
\begin_inset Formula $S$
\end_inset

).
